THE NUMBER GUESSING GAME!!!
How the game works:

1...Gameplay: You'll have 7 attempts to guess the randomly generated number between 1 and 100.
After each guess, you'll receive feedback whether your guess was too low, too high, or correct.

Features
Random Number Generation: The game selects a random number each time you play.
Limited Attempts: Players have a limited number of attempts (7) to increase the challenge.
Feedback Mechanism: After each guess, players receive helpful feedback.
Replay Option: Players can choose to play multiple rounds without restarting the program.
